titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 2,4-Diamino-3-Y4-(2-sulfoxyethylsulfonyl)-phenylazo?-5-Y4-(2 sulfoxyethyl sulfonyl)-2-sulfophenylazo?-benzenesulfonic acid potassium sodium salt.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary:
12/11/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,4-Diamino-3-Y4-(2-sulfoxyethylsulfonyl)-phenylazo?-5-Y4-(2 sulfoxyethyl sulfonyl)-2-sulfophenylazo?-benzenesulfonic acid potassium sodium salt.
